{"body": "You can archive the same behavior with:\n\n```erb\n<%= form_tag('/products', method: 'post', remote: true) do %>\n    <div id=\"product_errors\" style=\"display:none\"></div>\n    <%= button_tag 'Add field',  :class => 'add_field' %>\n    <%= text_field_tag 'mongoField', 'pcode' %>\n    <div id=\"mongoFields\"></div>\n    <br/>\n    <%= submit_tag 'Add/update' %>\n<% end %>\n```\n\n```javascript\n$(function() {\n  $('.add_field').click(function() {\n    $.addField($('#mongoField').val());\n\n    return false;\n  });\n});\n```\n\nI strongly recommend that you learn about unobtrusive javascript as I mentioned before in this pull request.", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/6473415", "created_at": "2012-06-21T03:30:55Z", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/5922#issuecomment-6473415", "updated_at": "2012-06-21T03:30:55Z", "repo": "rails", "issue_id": 5922, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/rafaelfranca", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://0.gravatar.com/avatar/0525b332aafb83307b32d9747a93de03?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2F2c7b84fa30f0cea96a90729afe2970a0.png", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca/received_events", "gravatar_id": "0525b332aafb83307b32d9747a93de03", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "login": "rafaelfranca", "type": "User", "id": 47848, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca/followers"}, "owner": "rails", "_i